description:
Data repository for the Human Lung Development Atlas: 
 &nbsp; 
 Preprint: https://doi.org/10.1101/2025.09.24.678382 
 &nbsp; 
 Github: https://github.com/GreenleafLab/HLDA 
 &nbsp; 
 This repository contains: 
 &nbsp; 
 lda_v2.rds: Seurat object of the whole human lung development atlas. Only contains gene expression count matrices.&nbsp; 
 Endothelial.rds, Epithelial.rds, Stromal.rds, Immune.rds: Subclustered Seurat objects to each compartment. Only contains gene expression count matrices.&nbsp;

